  "guidebook.chapter.NEA.Intro": "[center][font=dialogue]Introduction[/font][/center]
   
This first chapter of S&S introduces you to Mateo, a charming rogue with a sordid history. Unravel their connection to the Museum's missing contents, help them reconnect with the townsfolk, learn the Artificer skill, unlock the Underforge, the Arsenal system, and found a new branch of the Adventurer's Guild.",
  "guidebook.chapter.NEA.Mateo": "[nospacing]
[nextposition=0,10][center=300][font=dialogue]Mateo[/font][/center]
[offset=118,50][image=Characters/Mateo:0,0,16,32:4]
[offset=-118,144][center=300]Pronouns: They/Them[/center]
[offset=0,32][center=300]Birthday: Fall 25[/center]
[nextposition=322,16][image=Portraits/Mateo:0,0,64,64:4]
[nextposition=0,288]
[/nospacing]
Mateo is an experienced adventurer with a kind heart who grew up in Pelican Town. Not only are they a skilled Rogue, but they have an inclination for blacksmithing. A good leader and better friend who'll always have your back.",
"guidebook.chapter.NEA.Emeritus": "[nospacing]
[nextposition=0,10][center=300][font=dialogue]Emeritus[/font][/center]
[offset=90,50][image=Characters/MateoEmeritus:0,0,32,32:4]
[offset=-118,144][center=300]Pronouns: He/Him[/center]
[offset=0,32][center=300]Not Friendable[/center]
[nextposition=322,16][image=Portraits/MateoEmeritus:0,0,64,64:4]
[nextposition=0,288]
[/nospacing]
Emeritus is a jovial Pepper Rex who hatches with one goal: to protect East Scarp from the crab menace. He's the most loyal sidekick there is, and loves the occasional kiss on the forehead. He'll return it with bonus slobber!",
